{"tid":159881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】涂謹申指判刑合適 法院對七警或示威者一視同仁","createTime":"2017-03-17T10:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T16:43:56.000Z","uid":33053,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13dba8d200960e28649308d8ac7a2b5b08118093","tid":159881,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂中首宗暴動案件，三被告被裁定罪成今被判入獄三年，本身是律師的立法會議員涂謹申指，法庭的判決屬阻嚇性刑罰，他尊重法庭判決，認為判刑合適，又指法院一向對暴力案件認真嚴肅，不論被告是七警或是示威者均一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申又指，近年社會充斥撕裂情緒，政府近年施政埋下很多撕裂和不滿情緒，他希望未來政府能夠創造和諧氣氛。"},{"pid":"faa0ddfb37501dcb131bf4dc801cb056b90e8e67","tid":159881,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"賣港賊"},{"pid":"6cd141113a1447dcf081f3075e63768e64ee342d","tid":159881,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"111f9908c693e25b0efab50fb6d3f46105bec9b1","tid":159881,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb73c2108d48504c1204d4a532bb5353f97fd40f","tid":159881,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"涂撚申唔好搵次衝出黎柒得唔得呀？"},{"pid":"d11f7ab7479ea6b21e3bc9bcea070aed8a1419e2","tid":159881,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90e539abe7244d3e66dd8fcfd432609763d42c1","tid":159881,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"on9嘢唔想理...<br />\n返上去做政協啦"},{"pid":"246f2d8b00fce670367127a28bf76cf12c89792c","tid":159881,"uid":24